Moon Buggy is a simple game for the text mode in which you have to drive
your buggy across the moon's surface avoiding pits and blasting away 
any obstacles. With only two actions for the player (jump and blast) it is
really easy to learn but nevertheless very addictive.

Moon Buggy's Author is Jochen Voss
EOF
